{"tid":739196,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《銀魂2》真人劇   橋本環奈將飾演恐怖版神樂","createTime":"2018-07-12T02:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T02:41:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c0cdbee12c510e262b009034039952cd6a08af","tid":739196,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jBQoFo2mSzvRshy8zGtaeg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9ODQ4/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant/homerun/gameover.com.hk/4b309710e709c4744b6a911b6601e747\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjBQoFo2mSzvRshy8zGtaeg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9ODQ4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant%2Fhomerun%2Fgameover.com.hk%2F4b309710e709c4744b6a911b6601e747&h=d295580f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，真人電影《銀魂2》宣佈其衍生日劇《世界奇妙銀魂》將於8月18日在dTV上播出。一共有3話，包含失眠篇、土方禁菸篇和牙醫篇。<br />\n<br />\n這三篇都是非常搞笑的，其中在&ldquo;失眠篇&rdquo;中神樂的黑眼圈造型配上特別的睡眠故事也是把銀時下了個半死，有點心疼橋本環奈啊，感覺各位演員在這次的真人劇中又要被毀的很慘。<br />\n<br />\n在這部日劇中MADAO長穀川泰三終於登場，竟然是他的由動畫聲優立木文彥出演，看看這扮相真是&ldquo;本色&rdquo;出演了。話說土方禁菸篇和牙醫篇中有不少過激畫面，不知道電視劇會如何表現，不管怎麼樣估計都是能讓人從頭笑到尾了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180709/0/5/2/%E9%8A%80%E9%AD%822-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8A%87%E8%A9%B3%E6%83%85%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88-%E6%A9%8B%E6%9C%AC%E7%92%B0%E5%A5%88%E5%B0%87%E9%A3%BE%E6%BC%94%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E7%89%88%E7%A5%9E%E6%A8%82-9013042.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F0%2F5%2F2%2F%25E9%258A%2580%25E9%25AD%25822-%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258A%2587%25E8%25A9%25B3%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588-%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25A5%2588%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%25A3%25BE%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E7%2589%2588%25E7%25A5%259E%25E6%25A8%2582-9013042.html&d=p2Wq8BuHQnzrcShUu1WMwAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=a3306a46\" target=\"_b